{"tid":1218402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方清除路障時拘一女司機涉危駕","createTime":"2019-06-13T15:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T15:42:42.000Z","uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcdf7a347a2b150cc40563f6e1a3bcc50056e3a","tid":1218402,"uid":96854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"警方清除路障時拘一女司機涉危駕<br />\n2019/06/13 23:13<br />\n警方早上在夏愨道清除路障時發現一輛私家車，一名女司機涉嫌危險駕駛被捕。 <br />\n<br />\n該輛白色私家車打斜，停在夏愨道一條行車線上，警方指今早約九時清理夏愨道路障時，發現這輛車非法停留阻塞交通，調查後以涉嫌危險駕駛，拘捕一名二十八歲本地女司機，她正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/550523/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E6%99%82%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%B1%E9%A7%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F550523%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B8%2585%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259A%259C%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%25A7%2595&d=BIOOYiAB7dh8oRe%2BrusdWYhgI2KbCNwkzH4ce58ZUDE%3D&h=6e776af6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F550523%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25B8%2585%25E9%2599%25A4%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E9%259A%259C%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%258B%2598%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%258D%25B1%25E9%25A7%2595&h=21fa52a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/550523/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E6%B8%85%E9%99%A4%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C%E6%99%82%E6%8B%98%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E6%B6%89%E5%8D%B1%E9%A7%95</a>"}]}